snippet.title: Rude Racers Available on Pre-Order for Mac App Store
snippet.description:
#RudeRacers offers exciting bike #racing with crazy #fighting #action, mad weapons and fast #gameplay! Play through a tremendous variety of innovative challenges and establish yourself as the meanest racer on the street in this smashing new pick-up-and-play racer!

Special #MacOS version is now available for #PreOrderon the Mac #AppStore for just $1.99 featuring exclusive achievements and a new season!

https://apps.apple.com/us/app/1485412099

Pick up the definitive combat-racing game NOW!!

#FamousDogg #indieGame
